    "description": "<strong>命运在召唤黑马英雄<br>在一个童年假日里拯救一座陷入危机的岛屿。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/86d25222fe3da7b0fb302a5a8c4d17be.poster.avif?t=1720816442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/86d25222fe3da7b0fb302a5a8c4d17be.webm?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/86d25222fe3da7b0fb302a5a8c4d17be.mp4?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>眼看躁动的幽灵威胁着托罗米岛居民们的安全，泰必须冒险穿过危险的地牢和各种环境，来平息这些灵魂。这一切发生在一个暑假期间！<br><br>《Reverie》是一款动作冒险游戏，以一座虚构的新西兰岛屿为背景，其灵感源自《Maui and the Giant Fish》的传奇故事：半神半人的主人公用一只强大的鱼钩钓起了北岛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/1d5cd3a14e4f8270e64310e68ff329f5.poster.avif?t=1720816442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/1d5cd3a14e4f8270e64310e68ff329f5.webm?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/1d5cd3a14e4f8270e64310e68ff329f5.mp4?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>游戏特点：</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>穿过六座地牢，一路过关斩将，破解谜题。<br></li><li>使用独特的武器和道具解开谜题并打败气势汹汹的大头目。<br></li><li>探索千变万化的环境，找到托罗米岛的秘密。<br></li><li>收集隐藏的羽毛，它们来自新西兰众多美丽的本土鸟类。<br></li><li>故事灵感源自毛利人的传说。<br></li><li>游戏内成就系统<br></li><li>经过改进的全新道具选择<br></li><li>奖赏迷你游戏</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/0cb1df1745ae409f92ad0d08b5195e51.poster.avif?t=1720816442\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/0cb1df1745ae409f92ad0d08b5195e51.webm?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301100/extras/0cb1df1745ae409f92ad0d08b5195e51.mp4?t=1720816442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
